dct_description_sm: Map of the twelve tribes of Israel. Title cartouche shows the High Priest with candelabrum and an angel playing a harp. Relief shown pictorially. From Atlas moderne ... / par plusieurs auteurs. Paris : Lattré, 1771-1783. Publication date from dealer's notes. Along right side: Remarques, and Analyse succincte de la carte. "No. 35."
